{"tid":1764193,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"行動post 呢?","createTime":"2019-12-01T02:36:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T03:13:50.000Z","uid":335003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0ee88e1ae1fc259d75537f3c391d7b24cd0283e8","tid":1764193,"uid":335003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T02:36:36.000Z","msg":"今日有2個大遊行喎， 你想去邊個都好。<br />\n<br />\n啲行動post 唔係連熱門都 上唔到1個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />??<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">快啲推返個上嚟， 其他嘢用不推文啦。</span></span><br />\n定係大家都已經唔想出? 諗下我哋未贏返個熟悉嘅香港返嚟㗎， popo濫用暴力唔會因為區選贏咗有魔法變成無問題㗎。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要keep 住 撐落去阿大家!!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今期和理非手足繼續聚人氣參加集會遊行，負責勇武嘅手足我見到有好多人話啲路線好難走。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n勇武幾時開始會去認真考慮預約被捕書嘅詳細資訊㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />? 參考和理行進路線，其他嘢自己同自己team 計劃啦。<br />\n<br />\n普通人識叫咩叫不反咩？ 有同無都唔知咩嚟嘅，大會遊行路線我得閒慢慢去研究咩，靜係知有遊行就鳩出咋。<br />\n大概係咁，應該係咁，大概應該係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa2c6e8e4e1809d3f2ad0552b80b61a082c267c","tid":1764193,"uid":299647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T03:13:50.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借黎宣傳下，推比文宣組睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［廣告界不是condom] 推2號開始黎明行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1764022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1764022</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}